OL,6,FPC Luke Hobbs said: "The HGV gives us
OL,7,Fan elevated view into vehicles using
OL,8,Fthis busy stretch of road so we can
OL,9,Fbetter detect offences such as mobile
OL,10,Fphone use.
OL,12,F"Whilst the majority are law abiding
OL,13,Fdrivers, it is always shocking to see
OL,14,Fjust what some of these drivers think
OL,15,Fthey can get away with, all whilst in
OL,16,Fcontrol of a vehicle which can be up
OL,17,Fto 44 tonnes in weight with the
OL,18,Fpotential to cause significant and
OL,19,Fserious harm to others.
