OL,6,F"Last week alone, we saw drivers
OL,7,Fwatching films on their phones or
OL,8,Ftablets whilst behind the wheel,
OL,9,Foverloaded vehicles which can pose a
OL,10,Freal danger to other road users, and
OL,11,Fdrivers showing a complete disregard
OL,12,Ffor the speed limit."
OL,14,FIn total, 83 people were stopped -
OL,15,Fmainly for using a mobile phone or not
OL,16,Fwearing a seatbelt.
