OL,6,FActing Inspector Will Ayres of the
OL,7,FRoads Policing Unit said: "This
OL,8,Foperation coincided with a trial of
OL,9,Fnew Artificial Intelligence cameras,
OL,10,Fbeing rolled out by National Highways
OL,11,Fto spot drivers failing to wear
OL,12,Fseatbelts or using mobile phones.
OL,14,F"It is hoped the presence of these
OL,15,Fcameras will help enhance the work of
OL,16,Four Roads Policing Unit and further
OL,17,Freduce the number of individuals
OL,18,Ftaking risks when driving and causing
OL,19,Fserious collisions.
